01:32:22.202 --> 01:32:23.502
They're really heterogeneous

1587
01:32:24.922 --> 01:32:28.422
in the cancer cells, the expression of these virus proteins.

1588
01:32:29.502 --> 01:32:32.712
Yeah, I think that would be a selection criteria is you would need the

