01:33:10.502 --> 01:33:14.282
Obviously, ligand ability is a key criteria but not the only

1603
01:33:14.342 --> 01:33:15.002
criteria.

1604
01:33:16.082 --> 01:33:17.862
We oftentimes have profiled

1605
01:33:18.862 --> 01:33:22.422
hundreds of ubiquitin ligases in

1606
01:33:22.522 --> 01:33:26.342
assays, for example, to see whether we induce them in proximity with

